article:
This alphabetically arranged 'list of [[air force]]s' identifies the current and
historical names and roundels for the military aviation arms of countries
fielding an air component, whether an independent air force, a naval air arm,
army aviation unit, or coast guard. At the end is a separate list of no longer
extant nations that once operated air forces. Country names in italics indicate
that they are not generally recognized internationally as independent states but
which nonetheless managed to field an active air service. For information on the
size of air forces, see list of countries by size of armed forces. __NOTOC__
